body:
Hi @ymodak I've attached a small minimal module that reproduces the problem in the Jetson TX2, let me know if I can be of help.

There are two python modules one that creates the tensorrt graph and serializes it. the other try to run inference on an image. .

[tensorrt_problem.tar.gz](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/2516567/tensorrt_problem.tar.gz)
